        <div class="col-lg-4">

            <!--Dreamcast-->

            <img class="rounded-circle" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/teepublic/image/private/s--aDtUKHpN--/c_crop,x_10,y_10/c_fit,h_727/c_crop,g_north_west,h_1038,w_1038,x_-173,y_-156/l_upload:v1565806151:production:blanks:vdbwo35fw6qtflw9kezw/fl_layer_apply,g_north_west,x_-284,y_-267/b_rgb:484849/c_limit,f_auto,h_630,q_auto:good:420,w_630/v1575071875/production/designs/6953856_0.jpg" alt="Sega Dreamcast" width="140" height="140">
            <h2>The Sega Dreamcast</h2>
            <p>Was the first-ever video game console to have online functionality, released in 1999.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dreamcast" role="button">Learn more about the Dreamcast</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">

            <!--Minecraft-->

            <img class="rounded-circle" src="https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/866b6140-6e65-48fe-82b8-09d1c6dfcde3/d9hlkmq-f228b3fc-dd24-421b-8e60-0a4dadc17f46.jpg?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..cDwaTAxOJkydt9ivcNTvBjvuZr7xOi6wpSqADqtDP6E" alt="Minecraft" width="140" height="140">
            <h2>Minecraft</h2>
            <p>Is the highest-selling video game of all time, at over 300 million copies sold worldwide.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://www.minecraft.net/en-us" role="button">Check out Minecraft!</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">

            <!--PS2-->

            <img class="rounded-circle" src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51-toNb6MzL.jpg" alt="PS2" width="140" height="140">
            <h2>The PlayStation 2</h2>
            <p>Is the highest-selling video game console of all time at 155 million, with the Nintendo DS following closely behind at 154.02 million.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://www.playstation.com/en-us/ps5/" role="button">Buy a PlayStation5</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
